    "Conversely, if MOS predictors become very accurate and interpretable, we can consider using them as psychoacoustic tools to better understand human perception of speech.",
    "In the long term, we aim to be able to comprehensively model human preferences about synthesized speech, including arbitrary aspects of human opinions, and to be able to use those predictions during model development to produce the next generation of more realistic, diverse, and context-adaptable synthesized speech.",
